summary:
- **All resolutions passed**, including:  
  - Increase in authorised capital (Resolution 2)  
  - Ratification of prior share issues under Listing Rules 7.1 and 7.1A (Resolutions 4–5)  
  - Approval for director participation in placements (Resolutions 6–7)  
  - Share issuance in lieu of directors’ fees (Resolutions 8–10)  
  - Adoption of Employee Securities Incentive Plan (Resolution 11)  
  - Approval of incentive performance rights for directors (Resolutions 12–14)  
  - Renewal of 7.1A placement capacity mandate (Resolution 15).  

*No immediate trading or capital structure impacts identified; routine governance approvals.*
